---
title: Vegetarian Paella with Sweet Peppers, Mushrooms, and Rosemary
description: Paella, the national dish of Spain, is famous for its socarrat, the crispy crust that develops on the bottom of the pan. This version is flavored with woodsy rosemary and smoky paprika for a unique flavor. Vibrant turmeric adds gorgeous color.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegetarian-paella-2661790f.jpg
